name: Universal Reporting Device Bob U.R.D.B
description:
"This intergalactic communication device monitors 99% of the entire known area of the universe and connects to any other device in this territory, also connects on the internet, has video game function and know how to cook."



this work was created in the pixelpetz game by me (@eitaivan). i produced a series of original alien characters, exploring linking science fiction, fantasy and horror references.
